title: BasketballFranchises
name: BasketballFranchises
description: Placemarks for professional basketball franchises in the United States and Canada associated with the National Basketball Association, including the historic BAA (the NBA's predecessor), the ABA (a rival league that merged with the NBA), and the more recent minor league NBA Development League (or "D-League").  Placemarks are precise to the home city, not the home stadium.  For regional teams/teams shared by multiple cities, effort was made to choose the best single placemark.
